                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18261026-160-victim996 t18261026-160-viclabel885"></join>, in Bagnige Wells-road, and am a <rs id="t18261026-160-viclabel886" type="occupation">widow</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18261026-160-victim996 t18261026-160-viclabel886"></join>. On the 28th of September I was at my back window, and saw the prisoner about a hundred yards off, in the road, with this carpet under his arm - I sent my man after him, who brought him back with it - it is mine, and was tied to the door with a rope.</p>
